<p><b>Grant Morrison</b> (born January 31, 1960) is a <a href="/wiki/Scotland" title="Scotland">Scottish</a> <a href="/wiki/Comic_book" title="Comic book">comic book</a> writer and artist. He is best-known for his <a href="/wiki/Nonlinear_(arts)" title="Nonlinear (arts)" class="mw-redirect">nonlinear</a> <a href="/wiki/Narrative" title="Narrative">narratives</a> and <a href="/wiki/Counterculture" title="Counterculture">counter-cultural</a> leanings.</p>
